#: src/case-studies/case-study-stories.ts
msgid "The bet is *paying off*"
msgstr "그 베팅은 *결실을 맺고 있습니다*"

#. js-lingui-id: NT2bSJ
#: src/case-studies/case-study-stories.ts
msgid "The bet is paying off"
